# Claude
# CLAUDE.md is COMMITTED — shared, public-safe agent instructions (a portfolio plus).
# Personal/transient notes go in CLAUDE.local.md (gitignored).
# .claude/ is gitignored EXCEPT the Tier-1 canonical-facts files (committed): CONTEXT.md +
# KNOWN_ISSUES.md. The SESSION.md baton (and everything else in .claude/) stays local. (ADR-001.)
CLAUDE.local.md
.claude/*
!.claude/CONTEXT.md
!.claude/KNOWN_ISSUES.md
# Local-only convention gates that depend on a private tooling repo — never shared (see ADR-001).
.pre-commit-config.cpc.yaml

